OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRather
OL,6,Fcloudy with a few breaks offering some
OL,7,Fbright or sunny spells to end the day.
OL,8,FRemaining dry overnight with some
OL,9,Fclear spells at times, and light
OL,10,Fwinds. Frost-free with a few mist and
OL,11,Ffog patches.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FA bright start on Wednesday
OL,14,Fmorning, particularly in the east.
OL,15,FTurning increasingly cloudy into the
OL,16,Fafternoon, though staying largely dry
OL,17,Facross the region. Some rain during
OL,18,Fthe late evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
